race.comment: The speedy THINKING SENSATION (7) has had one blip in a string of narrow defeats. Has the inside barrier and may get a soft lead. Finds the right race, and the gelding will take a stack of catching. PETROULA (11) is third-up and hasn't been having the best of it. Has the outside gate to manage, but has pieces of form that would see her in the finish. MORAL TURPITUDE (5) peaks today and was slow off and wide here last time. It was a much better effort, and there's more up the sleeve. HE'S ELECTRIC (3) resumes, and the jumpouts have been good. Has a soft gate and handy 2kg claim. Everything points to improvement.
